		<td><b>Is the NES the &quot;glitchiest&quot; system?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It seems like it was acceptable for NES games to have scrolling and scanline glitches, but not so much for the SNES and Genesis era games.  Are there any other old systems that were known for having graphical glitches, besides the NES?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


