		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The Atari 2600 had the &quot;comb&quot; at left and even more sprite flicker than the NES.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
