	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The Apple II had pretty glitchy games, due to lack of vsync and it only having bitmapped graphics with a relatively slow CPU. Sound was likewise pretty rough.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


